# MCP Configuration

> ⚠️ **Important**: Do not commit sensitive tokens in this file!
> 
> For GitHub MCP server configuration, please see:
> https://docs.github.com/zh/copilot/how-tos/provide-context/use-mcp/set-up-the-github-mcp-server

## Example Configuration

```json
{
  "servers": {
    "github": {
      "type": "http",
      "url": "https://api.githubcopilot.com/mcp/",\      "requestInit": {
        "headers": {
          "Authorization": "Bearer YOUR_GITHUB_PAT_HERE"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

## Setup Instructions

1. Create a GitHub Personal Access Token
2. Replace `YOUR_GITHUB_PAT_HERE` with your actual token
3. Add this file to `.gitignore` to prevent accidental commits

